OL,3,CMan in his 30s killed in collision on
OL,4,CA5
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man has been killed
OL,7,Ffollowing a two-vehicle crash in the
OL,8,FGarvaghy area.
OL,10,FShortly before 10:15pm on Monday
OL,11,Fevening police received a report of
OL,12,Fthe collision involving a white Audi
OL,13,FA6 and silver Nissan Micra on the
OL,14,FOmagh Road, A5.
OL,16,FA PSNI spokesperson said officers
OL,17,Fresponded to the collision alongside
OL,18,Fcolleagues from other emergency
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
