OL,3,CMan in his 30s killed in collision on
OL,4,CA5
OL,6,F"Sadly, the driver of the Nissan Micra
OL,7,Fwas pronounced deceased at the scene,"
OL,8,Fthe spokesperson said.
OL,10,F"Medical treatment was provided to the
OL,11,Fthree occupants of the Audi A6 who
OL,12,Fwere then taken onward to hospital for
OL,13,Ftreatment to injuries not believed to
OL,14,Fbe life-threatening.
OL,16,F"The Omagh Road, between Ballygawley
OL,17,Fand Omagh which was closed in both
OL,18,Fdirections as we conducted a forensic
OL,19,Fexamination overnight and into this
OL,20,Fmorning, has now fully re-opened."
